casebody.data:
No. 677. George H. Allen et al., Petitioners, v. Nannie Field, Executrix, etc., et al. April 16, 1906. Mr. Levy Mayer, Mr. Alfred S. Austrian and Mr. Allan McCulloh for petitioners. Mr. Wm. Lindsay and Mr. J. Culbert Palmer for respondents.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.
